metadata.name: Cyberspace (Edition)
metadata.description:
The delicate balance of light and dark found in Cyberspace, a place where there are no rules, makes this new world as appealing as it is for many. Some citizens choose to lurk in the shadows while others choose to spread the light. Cyberspace is where the anti-heroine creates a place for herself and ushers in the new era.

This photo was taken from the roof of the second tallest in the United States.

Edition: 25/25
